        <div class="list-card">
          <h3>Roosevelt School District 66 leads</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Program ownership and all final decisions</li>
            <li>Claims submission to your state agency</li>
            <li>Vendor approvals and contract authority</li>
            <li>Community relationships and program direction</li>
            <li>Full authority as the approved SFSP sponsor</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
