      <div class="spotlight">
        <h3>We start small</h3>
        <p>
          Every new delivery program can begin with a focused onboarding phase — a smaller group of families over the first one to two weeks — before expanding. That gives your team time to get comfortable, confirm everything is working, and adjust if needed before moving to a larger scale.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.82);">
          You do not have to commit to full scale on day one to see what this could look like in practice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

