  <section class="section white">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="label">One more thing built into the partnership</div>
      <h2>Coordinated Purchasing Across the RuralBites Network</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        Roosevelt School District 66 should not have to manage procurement pressure alone while also trying to expand access for families.
      </p>

      <div class="spotlight">
        <h3>Coordinated Purchasing Across the RuralBites Network</h3>
        <p>
          As a RuralBites partner, Roosevelt School District 66 has access to coordinated purchasing across a broader network of programs, structured in alignment with federal and state procurement requirements.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);">
          This helps maintain competitive pricing and reduces the burden of managing procurement independently.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.82);font-size:.94rem;">
          This is built into the partnership — not an additional service.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
